        <comment><![CDATA[Process payments methods, <br/><br/><b>Issuers Bank/Installment Terms.</b><br/>Input the desired Installment Terms. Separate with comma.<br/>example: 3 months, 6 months, 10 months<br/>eg: 3, 6, 10]]></comment>
